    "taxonomy": "Porroglossum amethystinum is classified as a species of orchid in the genus Porroglossum. It belongs to the family Orchidaceae and is a type of epiphytic orchid. This classification places it within the order Asparagales and the clade monocots. Further classification within the kingdom Plantae groups it with flowering plants and vascular plants. At the rank of kingdom, Porroglossum amethystinum is classified as a member of the kingdom Plantae.",
